           SHORT="A modular screen saver and locker for X"

cat << EOF
XScreenSaver is a modular screen saver and locker for the X Window System.
It is highly customizable and allows the use of any program that can draw on
the root window as a display mode. More than 160 display modes are included
in this package.
EOF
